Perl script to dowload daily newspaper De Standaard.

Needed from CPAN:
WWW::Mechanize;
HTML::Form;
Getopt::Std;

Currently supported command-line options are:
-D: Get the whole daily newspaper
-v: Get the part Vooraan in de krant
-b: Get the part Binnenland en buitenland
-o: Get the part Opinie & Analyse
-s: Get the part Sport
-e: Get the part Economie
-u: Get the part Beurs

Examples:
Get everything:
./getstandaard -D
Get only Vooraan in de krant
./getstandaard -Dv
Get Sport and Economie
./getstandaard -Dse

Furthermore, this script still relies on joinPDF which you can find here: http://www.iis.ee.ic.ac.uk/~g.briscoe/
Alternatives are more than welcome.

